description:
&lt;p&gt;Circle Health is a company that runs hospitals and health services in the UK. We were founded in 2004, and we are different to most healthcare organisations for three reasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We have an open and honest culture, which allows our employees to feel empowered and a Circle credo which all our employees are aligned to.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We run healthcare in a new way: we put front-line clinicians, doctors and nurses in charge. By giving them responsibility and freedom, we believe they will run more effective, safe and caring services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And finally, we run some completely new types of service. We built independent hospitals which pioneered five-star hospitality in the UK, and we’re the only organisation running some innovative types of work in the NHS, like our Bedfordshire musculoskeletal contract.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role &amp; Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working flexibly, as part of the community services clinical team, to provide the highest standards of nursing care to our patients; to maintain high standards of communication throughout clinics, and to make a positive contribution towards the team’s pursuit of excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full time 37.5 hours per week- part time considered&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Person Specification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in a similar role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NMC registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A calm, caring and empathic attitude towards patients, relatives &amp; colleagues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An ability to communicate effectively with people at all levels,  with a commitment to collaborative working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent standard of patient care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27 Annual Leave with additional days after qualifying period&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cycle to Work Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pension Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee Assistance Programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private Medical Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-contributory Life Assurance and Income Protection Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee discounts platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Childcare Vouchers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season Ticket Loan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
